{"tid":593953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係德國] 漢諾威法院宣判，德國福士汽車公司必須讓極端分子復職","createTime":"2018-03-15T12:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T08:24:59.000Z","uid":41243,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"93ef790d4ea17307bf7d01033a0498286bbfcc4a","tid":593953,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:00:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5494085/Volkswagen-ordered-instate-suspected-Islamist-fired.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-5494085%2FVolkswagen-ordered-instate-suspected-Islamist-fired.html&d=tlv2LMwuHyvCW5WbeHa9MiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ae9b6590\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5494085/Volkswagen-ordered-instate-suspected-Islamist-fired.html</a> <br />\n德國真係獲獲新鮮獲獲甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n漢諾威法院宣判，德國福士汽車公司必須讓極端分子復職！<br />\n由於參與恐怖組織活動和威脅公司同事，德國福士汽車公司於 2016年將 極端分子 Samir B. 解僱<br />\n據德國大眾公司指出，這名極端分子多次前往敘利亞參加聖戰，並是Wolfsburg 地區極端組織的成員。他還曾經向大眾公司的同事發出 ''你們都得死！'' 的威脅！所以公司為安全理由將他解僱!<br />\n//Volkswagen's lawyers said was proven that Samir B. 'was involved in the recruitment and support of Islamic fighters from Wolfsburg', and that the company had no alternative but to terminate his employment.<br />\n<br />\n在審訊期間，福士公司曾提出補償這名極端分子65000歐元以換取他放棄復職的要求，但遭拒絕！<br />\n最後，法院作出判決: 德國福士公司的解僱無效！<br />\n福士汽車公司有義務一個月內將這人復職, 但報導指福士汽車公司正準備上訴..."},{"pid":"2ba60b43142811dd6cc6a8c5e16f9b913c090c0d","tid":593953,"uid":63017,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:05:09.000Z","msg":"其實個官都係極端組織既人"},{"pid":"9c514a41d0a78655c6e87275843bb285e18c1959","tid":593953,"uid":123956,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:25:23.000Z","msg":"個官唔是奸細"},{"pid":"4e4050b81b43d3f5cb4efe538ed538e5117ec462","tid":593953,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T12:35:30.000Z